Package com.intellij.psi.formatter.java.wrap

Interface ReservedWrapsProvider

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractJavaBlock, BlockContainingJavaBlock, CodeBlockBlock, CommentWithInjectionBlock, DocCommentBlock, ExtendsListBlock, LabeledJavaBlock, PartialWhitespaceBlock, SimpleJavaBlock, TextBlockBlock

    public interface ReservedWrapsProvider
    Defines contract for using predefined reserved wraps.

    Note: this interface is introduced for encapsulating legacy AbstractJavaBlock.getReservedWrap(IElementType) method and most probably will be removed as soon as formatting stuff is refactored.
